# Cloudflare Pages — Redirects & rewrites
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# Cloudflare Pages serves /terms automatically from terms.html (clean URLs
# are built in for files matching the path). Entries below cover URL
# variations a reader might guess by hand.

# Protected landings — force the .html form to the clean URL so they always
# pass through the protection Function (never served as a raw static file).
/breath-report.html   /breath-report   301
/breath-report-b.html /breath-report-b 301
/breath-report-c.html /breath-report-c 301
/nerve-report.html    /nerve-report    301

# Privacy aliases
/privacy        /privacy-policy        301
/privacidade    /privacy-policy        301

# Terms aliases
/terms-of-use   /terms                 301
/tos            /terms                 301

# Common 404 typo redirects (kept short — Pages already handles 404.html)
/home           /                      301
/index          /                      301
/index.html     /                      301
